                    <h6 class="section-title bg-white text-start text-primary pe-3 mt-4 mt-lg-0">Insurance Products</h6>
                    <div class="section-title-line"></div>
                    <p>Insurance is an essential part of any comprehensive financial plan, offering protection against
                        unexpected life events that can have a significant financial impact. Ratnesh Wealth Partners
                        provides a wide range of insurance products to cater to the various needs of our clients.
                        Whether you are looking for life insurance, health insurance, term insurance, or general
                        insurance, we offer tailored solutions designed to protect you, your family, and your assets.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">Life insurance, especially term insurance, is a financial tool that offers
                        protection to your loved ones in the event of your untimely demise. This type of insurance
                        provides a lump sum payout to the beneficiaries, helping them maintain their financial
                        well-being and meet their future expenses. At Ratnesh Wealth Partners, we help you assess your
                        life insurance needs by considering factors like your dependents, existing liabilities, and your
                        long-term financial goals. Our expert advisors will guide you in selecting the right coverage
                        and premium options that suit your individual situation.</p>
                    <p class="mb-4">Health insurance is another crucial aspect of financial security. With rising
                        medical costs and the unpredictability of health emergencies, having comprehensive health
                        coverage is essential. We provide access to a range of health insurance policies that offer
                        coverage for hospitalization, surgeries, critical illnesses, and even preventive care. Our
                        advisors help you choose the right plan based on your medical history, lifestyle, and the
                        healthcare coverage you require.</p>
                    <p class="mb-4">In addition to life and health insurance, we also offer general insurance products,
                        including property, vehicle, and home insurance, to protect your assets from unexpected losses
                        or damage. At Ratnesh Wealth Partners, we ensure that you and your family are adequately
                        covered, giving you peace of mind knowing that you are financially protected in times of need.
                    </p>

